        @Nonnull
public GraphVizEdge edge(@Nonnull
                                  GraphVizObject<?> source,
                                  @Nonnull
                                  GraphVizObject<?> target,
                                  @CheckForNull
                                  Object edgeId)
        Ensures that this graph contains a given edge.
        Parameters:
        source - The source node of the edge.
        target - The target node of the edge.
        edgeId - An optional identifier for this edge, allowing for multigraphs.
        Returns:
        Either an existing, or a newly created edge.
